details.description: Founded in 1992 in Taipei, Taiwan, Sharetea is a leading global bubble tea brand serving premiere authentic bubble tea. We offer a wide variety of fresh, high-quality drinks that blend premium tea with perfectly crafted tapioca pearls and other delicious toppings. Sharetea’s menu features an extensive range of beverages, including classic milk teas, premium fruit teas, and refreshing slushes. Our drinks come in a variety of customizable options, allowing customers to adjust sweetness levels, ice amounts, and toppings to suit their personal preferences. Whether you're craving one of our delectable milk teas, refreshing fruit teas, or savory slushes, we have the drink for you

reviews_data.review_text: Service was great! Braxtynn and team were very friendly and made my daughters and I love the experience. Will be back for sure!

reviews_data.review_text: Lost out on 12 pts… I would suggest asking people for their number before taking their order. 1) so they will get their points and 2) to promote and enroll new patrons.

We’re sorry to hear that and will take the opportunity to speak with the team as we want to ensure every guest gets their rewards points upon each visit! If you email us at sharetealkn@gmail.com we’ll make sure you get your points adjusted. Hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: The employees lily and hilliana were fantastic. They were super friendly and knew everything about boba! Totally recommend coming here.

reviews_data.review_text: Great customer service!  Stopped in to try out the tea and was greeted by a wonderful lady who allowed me to take a couple samples.  She also explained the teas to me as it was my first visit.  I ordered the Mango Green Tea and it taste fantastic!

reviews_data.review_text: Staff was great explaining the menu and the different options. Try it out when you are in the area, you will definitely come back!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Fabian, thank you for your review! So glad to hear you enjoyed your experience with the staff, store, drink, and the games! Hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: They were so kind & the drinks were delicious! It’s a very chill atmosphere.

reviews_data.review_text: If you haven't had boba tea before I would 100% recommend stopping by! And if you're someone who is already a fan of boba- Sharetea is a must have. reviews_data.owner_answer: John, we appreciate your review and so glad that you and the family had a great experience!

reviews_data.review_text: Ordered the coffee milk tea w/ coffee jelly and it was delicious. Beautiful location, games for kids, fair prices. Met the owner and his family today, wonderful people. Definitely made it a memorable experience. 10/10, will absolutely be coming back time and time again.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Charlotte, thank you so much for coming in! I enjoyed meeting you.

reviews_data.review_text: The new location is beautiful! It is so clean and they are so welcoming.  I love the bar area too! Drinks are amazing as they are in Cornelius.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Casey, thank you for your review and comments about the decor and our staff being welcoming! Well value every guest that visits us and want their experience to be of the highest quality. Hope to see you again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Sharetea is finally open in Mooresville. I’ve been waiting a long time for this. The staff are friendly, and the drinks are consistently excellent—10 out of 10. Highly recommended.
